solution:
Each number from 1 to 6 has probability $\dfrac{1}{6}$ of being rolled, so the expected value is \begin{align*}
\frac{1}{6}(6-1)&+\frac{1}{6}(6-2)+\frac{1}{6}(6-3)+\frac{1}{6}(6-4)+\frac{1}{6}(6-5)+\frac{1}{6}(6-6) \\
